<h1>About Bryan O'Connor</h1>


<p>
I created Own Your Taxes to help everyday Americans better understand taxes without needing a background in accounting or tax law.
</p>

<p>
Many small business owners, contractors, musicians, online sellers, and gig workers face the same challenge: tax information is often confusing and difficult to understand.
</p>

<p>
The Own Your Taxes series was created to make tax education more accessible by explaining important tax concepts in plain language with practical examples.
</p>

<p>
My goal is simple: help people gain confidence in their finances by understanding how taxes work and how to make better financial decisions throughout the year.
</p>

<h2>About the Book Series</h2>

<ul>
    <li>Small Business Edition</li>
